summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 73W page 173 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Lots 1-10 incl., Block 4, Robinson Tracts, located on east side of 38th Ave. So. between Othello St. and Myrtle St., from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) Zone to Community Business (BC) Zone.
